<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/779287-great-fictional-study-of-the-psychology-of">great fictional study of the psychology of the mob. all the characters are clearly depicted and reflected in their eagerness or reluctance to see three accused rustlers and murderers lynched before letting the law (as slow as it was) take its course. well done. what is the relationship between this book and the post civil war lynchings of black men?</a>
</div>
