<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11049401658778247487">Walter Van Tilburg Clark was an American novelist, short story writer, and educator. He ranks as one of Nevada&apos;s most distinguished literary figures of the 20th century and is known primarily for his novels, his one volume of stories, as well as his uncollected short stories. As a writer, he taught himself to use the familiar materials of the western saga to explore the human psyche and to raise d</span>
  <span id="freeText11049401658778247487" style="display:none">Walter Van Tilburg Clark was an American novelist, short story writer, and educator. He ranks as one of Nevada's most distinguished literary figures of the 20th century and is known primarily for his novels, his one volume of stories, as well as his uncollected short stories. As a writer, he taught himself to use the familiar materials of the western saga to explore the human psyche and to raise deep philosophical issues.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11049401658778247487" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

